title: Walking the path together - healing ceremony on 26 January | Manningham Council
description: Wurundjeri Woi-wurrong elders and Manningham Council host a meaningful, reflective, and respectful event in a demonstration of togetherness on 26 January.
cleaned_text: with Manningham Council, are hosting a meaningful, reflective, and respectful event in a demonstration of togetherness on 26 January. Hosted at MC Square, this event will be free and feature story-telling, music and art. It is open to everyone who would like to attend.
